data.description: This home has definitely the WOW factor! Recently renovated, including the HVAC and Roof!!! Sitting at the end of the cul de sac on a 4 acre lot, giving you privacy and endless possibilities!!  A favorite open floor plan with a bright stunning Gourmet kitchen and open dining and family room boasting a stone fireplace making it very inviting!  The primary bedroom and bathroom are very spacious and the secondary bedrooms are spacious too! In the lower level you will find a suite/room/office/gym, you can make it what you desire. It also has a full 3rd bathroom and plenty of storage! The multi-level deck is amazing and perfect for your outdoor activities! This home is perfect for entertaining or living a relaxed life. Conveniently located close to shopping, entertainment, Hwy. 985, restaurants,churches, parks! Great Schools!
